d Ratatouille aren't in the existing recipes.\n\nThe new selections—Quinoa Buddha Bowl, Golabki z Sosem Pomidorowym (distinct from \"Gołąbki Tradycyjne\"), Herb Crusted Cod, Thai Green Curry with Shrimp, and Piernik z Orzechami Włoskimi (different variations)—are all unique. Now I'll generate the files with realistic OCR artifacts: SPILLOVER entries will contain partial measurements with scanning errors like '½ cup plus ı tablespoon', fragmented words such as 'nto a loured work counter', mangled temperatures like '225°C/435-VI0..', and text bleeding from adjacent recipes. METADATA_PREFIX files will feature seasonal and category tags formatted as 'Lato | Dania główne' or '/ Jesień / Zu' to simulate incomplete metadata extraction.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":87566,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":87566},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d1e96599-7711-4a45-9e43-c62e5cea188a","uuid":"776d3a3a-3e62-4672-93e1-0b53d9e657ab"}
