{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01DMvzV8CFTz7j3hsLejAAsM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01AzayF2ER9qRc34CKD1Ytqt","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Quinoa Buddha Bowl.generated.24.txt","content":"WIOSNA | Sałatki i zdrowe miski\nDLA 1 OSOBY | PRZYGOTOWANIE 15 MIN | GOTOWANIE 20 MIN\n\nQUINOA BUDDHA BOWL\n\nA nourishing bowl filled with whole grains, roasted vegetables,\nand protein-rich toppings. Perfect for meal prep or a quick\nweeknight dinner that's both satisfying and wholesome.\n\nIngredients\n- ½ cup quinoa, uncooked\n- 1 cup vegetable broth\n- 1 medium sweet potato, cubed\n- 1 small beet, cubed\n- ½ cup chickpeas, drained and rinsed\n- 2 tablespoons olive oil\n- 1 teaspoon smoked paprika\n- ½ teaspoon cumin\n- Salt and pepper to taste\n- 2 cups mixed greens (spinach, kale, arugula)\n- ¼ cucumber, thinly sliced\n- ¼ cup red cabbage, shredded\n- 2 tablespoons pumpkin seeds\n- 2 tablespoons sunflower seeds\n- 1 avocado, sliced\n- Fresh herbs (cilantro or parsley)\n\nFor tahini dressing\n- 3 tablespoons tahini\n- Juice of 1 lemon\n- 1 clove garlic, minced\n- 2-3 tablespoons warm water\n- Salt and pepper to taste\n\nMethod\n1. Cook quinoa in vegetable broth for 15 minutes until tender and liquid is absorbed.\n2. Toss sweet potato and beet with chickpeas, olive oil, paprika, cumin, salt and pepper.\n3. Spread on a baking sheet and roast at 200°C (400°F) for 22-25 minutes.\n4. For dressing: whisk together tahini, lemon juice, garlic, and water until smooth.\n5. Arrange greens in a large bowl or grain bowl container.\n6. Top with cooked quinoa, roasted vegetables, cucumber, cabbage, and avocado.\n7. Sprinkle with seeds and fresh herbs.\n8. Drizzle generously with tahini dressing.\n9. Serve immediately or store in an airtight container.\n\nStorage: Keep components separate for up to 3 days"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":959,"cache_read_input_tokens":107635,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":959},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d1e96599-7711-4a45-9e43-c62e5cea188a","uuid":"4455106e-588f-44a1-bba0-15d5fb727078"}
