{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01NLFqWMLDtsEvz3MfsJQMYE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01PeTbRUWU5NByUWDDWFtufe","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Herb Crusted Cod.generated.24.txt","content":"SUMMER | Fish Mains\nSERVES 2 | PREP 10 MIN | COOK 15 MIN\n\nHERB CRUSTED COD\n\nA simple yet elegant fish dish that highlights the delicate\nflavor of cod. The herb crust locks in moisture while adding\nwonderful texture and aromatic depth.\n\nIngredients\n- 2 cod fillets (6 oz each), skin-on or skin-off\n- ¼ cup panko breadcrumbs\n- 3 tablespoons fresh parsley, finely chopped\n- 2 tablespoons fresh dill, finely chopped\n- 1 tablespoon fresh chives, finely minced\n- 1 tablespoon Parmesan cheese, finely grated\n- 2 cloves garlic, minced very finely\n- Zest of ½ lemon\n- 2 tablespoons olive oil\n- 1 tablespoon butter\n- Salt and freshly ground pepper to taste\n- Lemon wedges for serving\n- Fleur de sel for finishing\n\nMethod\n1. Pat cod fillets dry with paper towels. Season with salt and pepper.\n2. In a shallow bowl, combine panko, parsley, dill, chives, Parmesan, garlic, and lemon zest.\n3. In a small bowl, mix 1 tablespoon olive oil with the herb mixture to bind.\n4. Press herb crust gently onto the top of each cod fillet.\n5. Heat remaining olive oil and butter in a large skillet over medium-high heat.\n6. When butter is foaming, carefully place cod fillets crust-side up.\n7. Cook for 3-4 minutes until the bottom is golden and the fish begins to flake.\n8. Gently flip the fillets and cook for another 2-3 minutes until cooked through.\n9. The herb crust should be golden and fragrant.\n10. Transfer to a warm plate, finish with a pinch of fleur de sel.\n11. Serve immediately with lemon wedges and your choice of sides.\n\nSuggested sides: roasted asparagus, sautéed baby spinach, or new potatoes with dill"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1089,"cache_read_input_tokens":109392,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1089},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d1e96599-7711-4a45-9e43-c62e5cea188a","uuid":"04cdf8d9-ddda-49f1-840d-46dacf6cc944"}
